transcripts.text: Hello, hello!  I am so excited to be able to show you all Shop Disney's new Cinderella's Coach Wheelchair Cover Set by Disguise.  Here I am setting it up, which is fairly easy.  Just some velcro ties on the arms and back, followed by some above or on the tires.  I am so glad it will be available for any Disney-loving wheelchair user that loves to dress up and dreams of heading to the ball.  A big thank you to Shop Disney for sponsoring this video.
